{"tid":328260,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗又做老豆，今次有爺生有乸教","createTime":"2017-07-19T12:31:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T13:13:08.000Z","uid":84462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7014031a31bd9aac562eb802fa59ebf71d927130","tid":328260,"uid":84462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T12:31:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://football.fanpiece.com/m/offside/c1289692.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffootball.fanpiece.com%2Fm%2Foffside%2Fc1289692.html&d=knZUuThT10lE1RgPl8n9P7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=8f077aef\" target=\"_blank\">http://football.fanpiece.com/m/offside/c1289692.html</a><br />\nC朗今年在球場上頻頻大演帽子戲法，估唔到連生仔都連中三元，繼一子一女雙胞胎剛告誕生後，近日又有喜訊，模特兒女友佐珍娜宣告懷孕，現年32歲的C朗很快將做第四任父親，這亦將是C朗首次由正印女友為他誕下麟兒。<br />\n<br />\n正在度假中的C朗日前被傳媒拍到與22歲的女友佐珍娜在一起，女方被發現肚子出現異常的突起，因此傳出懷孕消息，有報道指佐珍娜懷孕已最少四個月。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙媒體《El Mundo》問C朗是否對女友有喜感到高興，C朗直言：「是的，非常高興。」<br />\n<br />\nC朗心情勁靚，對《El Mundo》談及剛滿月不久的龍鳳胎馬里亞及馬迪奧，形容他們「如珠如寶」，而且令他學會很多有關換尿片的知識，C朗表示自己做得不太好，但會努力嘗試。媒體報道兩子是C朗找代母所生。<br />\n<br />\nC朗還有一名正在小童隊受訓的六歲長子，據傳也是由代母所生，另外亦有傳是C朗一夜情的副產品。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">媒體報道佐珍娜已做過多次DNA測試，以證明其腹中塊肉是由C朗血脈所出。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.marca.com/en/football/real-madrid/2017/07/18/596e0a9e46163f9a7b8b46a5.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.marca.com%2Fen%2Ffootball%2Freal-madrid%2F2017%2F07%2F18%2F596e0a9e46163f9a7b8b46a5.html&d=knZUuThT10lE1RgPl8n9P7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=44be1785\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.marca.com/en/football/real-madrid/2017/07/18/596e0a9e46163f9a7b8b46a5.html</a><br />\n死臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b8fe8eb2fdc7873415c2d0defd4a8c8fe876ec","tid":328260,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T12:36:31.000Z","msg":"已做過多次DNA測試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"078d7531dc7cdc035d952b28e3d5c620d94d747c","tid":328260,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T12:37:04.000Z","msg":"牙朗都要同雞拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67b8f155dcfbf88bca453936ccb107db43a59351","tid":328260,"uid":50020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T12:44:07.000Z","msg":"幾識玩，唔結婚齋生"},{"pid":"61519617c25f8f3f6e6946f3d5506e4abcb08daa","tid":328260,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T12:54:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已做過多次DNA測試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2318634b84be520cd670378c28867907b40c26b7","tid":328260,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:13:08.000Z","msg":"條友不停生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個個老母都唔同"}]}